author: DarthVader_
title: Weird set.
review: This was a weird set.  I got it at McDonalds back in the day.  I still have some of the pieces.  It was a really wierd set!  I liked messing around with it.  Over all, it was a pretty boring set!  But, itleast it was free!

author: mvila09
title: This set shouldnt even exist.
review: I think this is one of my non favorite sets i have.Anyway,heres the pros.Pros free,i have it,snow board,Hey you get it with a happy meal.Cons no arm like the basketball green shirt,is that a hockey stick?,no parts are removable besides legs.***3 stars.

author: WiseWarrior
title: McDonalds should stick to normal legos
review: I got this 4 years ago and never liked it. It looks like some messed-up Duplo set, and I never liked Duplos much anyway. But, it was free, so I can't really complain. You can only get it off the internet now, but I wouldn't suggest it.
